2346: go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -coverprofile=coverage.out\n2347: go tool cover -html=coverage.out -o coverage.html\n2348: ```\n2349: \n2350: ## 结论\n2351: \n2352: 所有核心组件均有充分的单元测试覆盖，符合 >80% 覆盖率要求。\n2353: 所有 test_spec.md 中定义的测试用例均已验证通过。\n2354: ```\n2355: \n2356: **Step 5: Commit**\n2357: \n2358: ```bash\n2359: git add TEST_VERIFICATION.md\n2360: git commit -m \"test(ar-038): add test verification summary\"\n2361: ```\n2362: \n2363: ---\n2364: \n2365: ### Task 19: 最终验证和清理\n2366: \n2367: **Files:**\n2368: - None (verification task)\n2369: \n2370: **Step 1: Run complete test suite**\n2371: \n2372: ```bash\n2373: go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v -race -cover\n2374: ```\n2375: \n2376: Expected: All tests PASS with race detection\n2377: \n2378: **Step 2: Build the project**\n2379: \n2380: ```bash\n2381: go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...\n2382: ```\n2383: \n2384: Expected: Build succeeds\n2385: \n2386: **Step 3: Check for any missing test files**\n2387: \n2388: ```bash\n2389: find ./pkg/workloadmanager -name \"*.go\" ! -name \"*_test.go\" -type f\n2390: ```\n2391: \n2392: Ensure all .go files have corresponding test files\n2393: \n2394: **Step 4: Verify test naming conventions**\n2395: \n2396: ```bash\n2397: ls -la ./pkg/workloadmanager/*/*_test.go\n2398: ```\n2399: \n\n(Showing lines 2300-2399 of 2480. Use offset=2400 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"**Step 4: Create summary document**\n\n创建测试验证总结文档：\n\n```markdown\n# AR-038 测试验证总结\n\n## 测试用例验证\n\n### TestCase-WM-001: Sandbox 创建接口\n- ✅ TestSandboxController_CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox_Success\n- ✅ TestSandboxController_CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox_Success\n- 验证: 合法输入返回 200 OK 及 sessionId\n\n### TestCase-WM-002: Sandbox 幂等性\n- ✅ 通过控制器和 reconciler 验证\n- 验证: 相同 name 的幂等性\n\n### TestCase-WM-003: 非法输入拦截\n- ✅ TestSandboxController_CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox_InvalidInput_NoPodTemplate","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/tasks.m