structured.UnstructuredList{},\n39:     )\n40:     \n41:     fakeClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClientWithCustomListKinds(scheme, map[schema.GroupVersionResource]string{\n42:         SandboxGVR: \"SandboxList\",\n43:         SandboxClaimGVR: \"SandboxClaimList\",\n44:     })\n45: \n46:     sessionID := \"test-session\"\n47:     \n48:     mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, sessionID).Return(nil, fmt.Errorf(\"store error\"))\n49: \n50:     sandbox := buildTestSandbox(\"test-sandbox\", \"default\", sessionID, 24*time.Hour)\n\n(Showing lines 1-50 of 2480. Use offset=51 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038 Implementation Plan\n\n**Feature:** AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n**Goal:** 为 pkg/workloadmanager 模块编写全面的单元测试，确保所有核心组件、控制器、处理器和工具函数都有充分的测试覆盖。\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- 所有核心组件（controller、handler、client、gc、auth、middleware、config、api）都有对应的 *_test.go 文件\n- 测试覆盖率 >80%\n- 所有测试可通过 `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 运行\n- 测试遵循 testify/assert 和 mock 的使用模式\n- 测试用例覆盖正常流程、边界条件和错误场景\n- 遵循 test_spec.md 中定义的测试用例（TestCase-WM-001, TestCase-WM-002, TestCase-WM-003）\n**Architecture:** Go 单元测试，使用 testify 框架，fake k8s client\n**Tech Stack:** Go 1.21+, testify, k8s.io/client-go/testing\n**Frontend validation:** No\n\n---\n\n### Task 1: 验证现有测试并更新 gc/collector_test.go\n\n**Files:**","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775892959363,"end":1775892959378}}}}
